latestPosts.caption:
Neeraj & Aishwarya: A Timeless Union

Neeraj and Aishwarya’s love story blossomed amidst the elegance of tradition and the serenity of nature. Aishwarya stunned in a green Paithani saree, while Neeraj complemented her with a regal cream sherwani.

Their chemistry shone through every frame, from tender smiles to quiet moments of togetherness. The lush greenery symbolized the depth and steadiness of their bond, while their traditional attire celebrated the richness of their heritage.

In frame - @aishdingre @neerajchavan_ 
Makeup - @makeupartist_nikitakale
